com.mysema.query.group

Class GroupByBuilder<K>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mysema.query.group.GroupByBuilder<K>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - 

    public class GroupByBuilder<K>
extends Object
    GroupByBuilder is a fluent builder for GroupBy transformer instances. This class is not to be used directly, but via GroupBy.
    Author:
    tiwe
